  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct WindowSystemInfoXCB : public IRenderer::WindowSystemInfoBase;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowSystemInfoXCB</TypeRef> structure identifies the XCB window system and supplies the XCB connection used during renderer initialization.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Linux or compatible X11 platforms when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_XCB_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled. This is automatically enabled on Linux unless platform binding selection is manual.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
